title: Deeper Than You Think
description:
God wants to deal with our problems at the root.

In “Deeper Than You Think,” Pastor Steven Furtick shows us that God’s power at work within us is stronger than any circumstance we’re facing.

If you’ve just made a decision for Christ, please respond HERE: http://ele.vc/tIepfr
